"night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/494802462"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpJmNh/3An7h0EAMaCDcyMjM3MDQ0IIyF44sGMAI4lgJACHIJNDk0ODAyNDYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1635922951.6513655", "card_id": "Q_495295446", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 577}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在二三十岁的年轻人，外貌上的年龄特征没那么明显了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "不知道你有没有这种感觉，现在在路边看到一个不认识的人，基本很难凭借肉眼准确判断他的年龄大小。 或许是因为时尚的穿搭风格，或许是因为精致减龄的妆容，甚至是因为 TA 身上有少年少女气息… 为什么当代年轻人在外貌上的年龄特征变弱化了？这种现象背后的原因是什么呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-d3fbc778de8369784c567895a92f11a5_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "301 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495295446"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpJmNh/3An7h0EAMaCDcyMzQ2Nzk5IKKw7osGMAA49gVACXIJNDk1Mjk1NDQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1635922951.6519399", "card_id": "Q_496025552", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 502}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "图灵奖得主称中国高校过于看重国际声望，应更关注本科教学质量，本科教育应朝着什么方向努力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "第四届世界顶尖科学家论坛开幕式上，图灵奖得主约翰·霍普克罗夫特谈到本科生教育时表示，他发现中国的高校过于注重国际声望，把研究经费和论文数量作为重要的衡量指标。他认为，现在高质量的本科生数量远远无法达到社会需求，应该更关注如何提高所有学生的教学质量。图灵奖得主：中国高校应该更关注本科教学质量 - 观察者网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-f2ce4fc89ee10e3f82f50a3b4be5ad54_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "298 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/496025552"}}, "attached_info": "ClYIpJmNh/3An7h0EAMaCDcyNTA4ODMyIIeqgowGMIUBOI4aQApyCTQ5NjAyNTU1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1635922951.6526265", "card_id": "Q_496304840", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_