休，我本来满心欢喜期待的周六以后都要没了，现在在犹豫要不要辞职。 由于本人对这份工作并没有什么热情，加上由于部门职能关系，与业务部的同事一直相处不好，一度有点抑郁。现在上班多一分钟对我来说都是煎熬，周六周日是我唯一充电的时候，居然就这样要被无条件剥夺，犹如晴天霹雳，说着都有点想掉眼泪了。 现在很犹豫，如果公然反抗的话怕以后公司会想办法针对我，我觉得我的内心还不够强大，被针对很可能会马上受不了想走。但这样沉默接受我也无法接受，无条件加班真的太难受了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e31a7ccf56e1ffccc8b624405bd06027_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493992388"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpJmNh/3An7h0EAMaCDcyMDU3NDMyILnsy4sGMCc4ywRAL3IJNDkzOTkyMzg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1635922951.6754882", "card_id": "Q_293998045", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "清蒸鲈鱼应该怎么做？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e371e3d79e72aa73685d40594d13a757_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/293998045"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpJmNh/3An7h0EAMaCDI3NjEwMTU0IOqC1NwFMAA4rQFAMHIJMjkzOTk4MDQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1635922951.675946", "card_id": "Q_495275900", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "不看原著到底能不能看懂电影《沙丘》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2bc438601cffc0d526790baea08fb8dc_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495275900"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IpJmNh/3An7h0EAMaCDcyMzQyNDE3IMyN7osGMAI4SkAxcgk0OTUyNzU5MDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}